親愛的學生們：Dear students,     這個網站是我們計畫並討論 ”中國古代文明“ 專題作業的平臺。查閱本網站, 你們會進一步瞭解本專題作業的研究內容及相關指引。完成本專題作業後，你們必定會更瞭解中國古代文明。This Site is our communication platform to plan and share information
for the cultural project “Ancient Chinese Civilization".  From this Google Sites WebQuest, you can get tips for working on
your project.  After completing this project, you will understand more
about the Ancient Chinese Civilization.祝大家學習愉快！Wish you all enjoy learning Chinese language/culture. :) 黃老師 Huang Laoshi 





